(1142, 294, 'tenent_1', '1. We believe the <strong>Bible (King James translation)</strong> is the authenticated Word of God.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>II Timothy 3:16-17</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 22:18-19</li>\r\n	<li>Deuteronomy 4:1-8</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1143, 294, '_tenent_1', 'field_51e5c48970304'),
(1144, 294, 'tenent_2', '2. We believe in the <b>virgin birth of Jesus Christ</b> and that there is no salvation in any other name.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 1:20-22</li>\r\n	<li>Luke 1:26-27</li>\r\n	<li>Isaiah 7:14</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 4:11-12</li>\r\n	<li>Colossians 3:17</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1145, 294, '_tenent_2', 'field_51e5c4e270306'),
(1146, 294, 'tenent_3', '3. We believe in the <b>death, burial, resurrection, and ascension of Christ</b>.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Corinthians 15:3-5</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 13:28-31</li>\r\n	<li>Romans 6:3-10, 8:11</li>\r\n	<li>Mark 16:18-19</li>\r\n	<li>Luke 24:50-51</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 1:9-11</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1147, 294, '_tenent_3', 'field_51e5c4ef70307'),
(1148, 294, 'tenent_4', '4. We believe in <b>a born-again experience</b> from the old life in Adam to the new life in Jesus Christ.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 3:3</li>\r\n	<li>1 Corinthians 15:22</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1149, 294, '_tenent_4', 'field_51e5c4f770308'),
(1150, 294, 'tenent_5', '5. We believe in the <b>Baptism of the Holy Spirit</b> with the <b>evidence of speaking in other tongues</b>.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Acts 2:4, 10:45-46, 19:6</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1151, 294, '_tenent_5', 'field_51e5c50070309'),
(1152, 294, 'tenent_6', '6. We believe in the <b>Baptism of Water by immersion</b> and that it is essential to all believers, and must be administered by an ordained authority of the church.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 28:19</li>\r\n	<li>Mark 16:16</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 2:38</li>\r\n	<li>John 1:6, 15:16</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1153, 294, '_tenent_6', 'field_51e5c5087030a'),
(1154, 294, 'tenent_7', '7. We believe in the <b>Eternal Invisible God, the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ</b>.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 1:18</li>\r\n	<li>Colossians 1:15</li>\r\n	<li>I Timothy 1:17, 6:16 (father)</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 1:6</li>\r\n	<li>I Peter 1:3</li>\r\n	<li>Ephesians 1:2-3, 3:14</li>\r\n	<li>II Corinthians 1:3</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1155, 294, '_tenent_7', 'field_51e5c5127030b'),
(1156, 294, 'tenent_8', '8. We believe in the <b>Millennial Reign and Rule of Jesus Christ with his Bride</b> over the earth.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>II Timothy 2:12</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 2:26-27, 5:10, 12:5</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 19:15, 20:4</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1157, 294, '_tenent_8', 'field_51e5c5197030c'),
(1158, 294, 'tenent_9', '9. We believe in <b>the Second Coming</b> (soon) <b>of Jesus Christ for the reaping of his Bride</b> out of the Church.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Thessalonians 4:16-17</li>\r\n	<li>John 14:3</li>\r\n	<li>James 5:7</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 9:28</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 14:15-16</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1159, 294, '_tenent_9', 'field_51e5c5227030d'),
(1160, 294, 'tenent_10', '10. We believe in a<b> life of holiness and sanctification unto the Lord</b>, and only this class of people will reign with him.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>II Corinthians 7:1</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 12:14</li>\r\n	<li>I Thessalonians 5:23</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1161, 294, '_tenent_10', 'field_51e5c5297030e'),
(1162, 294, 'tenent_11', '11. We believe in the <b>Resurrection of the Dead</b>; both the Just and the Unjust.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 5:28</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 24:15</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1163, 294, '_tenent_11', 'field_51e5c5347030f'),
(1164, 294, 'tenent_12', '12. We believe in the <b>miracle working power of Jesus Christ through divine healing</b>; even after doctors have given up.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 8:2-8, 14-16, 28</li>\r\n	<li>Matthew 9:20</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1165, 294, '_tenent_12', 'field_51e5c53c70310'),
(1166, 294, 'tenent_13', '13. We believe in <b>eternal life</b> for the righteous and death for the wicked.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 25:46</li>\r\n	<li>John 5:29</li>\r\n	<li>Jude 7</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1167, 294, '_tenent_13', 'field_51e5c54470311'),
