(1338, 297, 'tenet_7', '7. We believe in the <strong>Eternal Invisible God, the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ.</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 1:18</li>\r\n	<li>Colossians 1:15</li>\r\n	<li>I Timothy 1:17, 6:16 (father)</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 1:6</li>\r\n	<li>I Peter 1:3</li>\r\n	<li>Ephesians 1:2-3, 3:14</li>\r\n	<li>II Corinthians 1:3</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1339, 297, '_tenet_7', 'field_51e5c5127030b'),
(1340, 297, 'tenet_8', '8. We believe in the <strong>Millennial Reign and Rule of Jesus Christ with his Bride</strong> over the earth.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>II Timothy 2:12</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 2:26-27, 5:10, 12:5</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 19:15, 20:4</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1341, 297, '_tenet_8', 'field_51e5c5197030c'),
(1342, 297, 'tenet_9', '9. We believe in <strong>the Second Coming</strong> (soon) <strong>of Jesus Christ for the reaping of his Bride</strong> out of the Church.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Thessalonians 4:16-17</li>\r\n	<li>John 14:3</li>\r\n	<li>James 5:7</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 9:28</li>\r\n	<li>Revelation 14:15-16</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1343, 297, '_tenet_9', 'field_51e5c5227030d'),
(1344, 297, 'tenet_10', '10. We believe in a<b> </b><strong>life of holiness and sanctification unto the Lord</strong>, and only this class of people will reign with him.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>II Corinthians 7:1</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 12:14</li>\r\n	<li>I Thessalonians 5:23</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1345, 297, '_tenet_10', 'field_51e5c5297030e'),
(1346, 297, 'tenet_11', '11. We believe in the <strong>Resurrection of the Dead</strong>; both the Just and the Unjust.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 5:28</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 24:15</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1347, 297, '_tenet_11', 'field_51e5c5347030f'),
(1348, 297, 'tenet_12', '12. We believe in the <strong>miracle working power of Jesus Christ through divine healing;</strong> even after doctors have given up.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 8:2-8, 14-16, 28</li>\r\n	<li>Matthew 9:20</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1349, 297, '_tenet_12', 'field_51e5c53c70310'),
(1350, 297, 'tenet_13', '13. We believe in <strong>eternal life</strong> for the righteous and death for the wicked.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 25:46</li>\r\n	<li>John 5:29</li>\r\n	<li>Jude 7</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1351, 297, '_tenet_13', 'field_51e5c54470311'),
(1352, 297, 'tenet_14', '14. We believe in the <strong>restoration of the Church;</strong> back to the same order of the Church that came out on the Day of Pentecost.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Acts 3:21</li>\r\n	<li>James 5:7</li>\r\n	<li>Hosea 6:3</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1353, 297, '_tenet_14', 'field_51e5c54a70312'),
(1354, 297, 'tenet_15', '15. We believe in <strong>marriage</strong> and that believers should have only <strong>companions of like precious faith</strong>.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Corinthians 6:14-18</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 13:4</li>\r\n	<li>I Timothy 5:14</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1355, 297, '_tenet_15', 'field_51e5c55170313'),
(1356, 297, 'tenet_16', '16. We believe in <strong>God’s divine government for the Church</strong> and that the Church is one body with apostles, prophets, evangelists, pastors, and teachers.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ephesians 4:11</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1357, 297, '_tenet_16', 'field_51e5c55770314'),
(1358, 297, 'tenet_17', '17. We believe in the <strong>best form of school</strong> on Sundays (not Sunday School) <strong>with an ordained ministry as teachers of the Bible,</strong> and that we must have an understanding of the Holy Writ.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Timothy 2:4</li>\r\n	<li>Proverbs 4:5-9</li>\r\n	<li>Colossians 1:9</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1359, 297, '_tenet_17', 'field_51e5c55e70315'),
(1360, 297, 'tenet_18', '18. We believe in a <strong>House of Prayer for all of God’s people</strong>, where God is no respector of persons.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Acts 10:34</li>\r\n	<li>Isaiah 56:7</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1361, 297, '_tenet_18', 'field_51e5c56870316'),
(1362, 298, 'core_belief_1', 'We believe in the virgin birth of Jesus Christ and that there is no salvation in any other name.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Matthew 1:20-22</li>\r\n	<li>Luke 1:26-27</li>\r\n	<li>Isaiah 7:14</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 4:11-12</li>\r\n	<li>Colossians 3:17</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1363, 298, '_core_belief_1', 'field_51e4774e02d1c'),
(1364, 298, 'core_belief_2', 'We believe in the death, burial, resurrection, and ascension of Christ.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>I Corinthians 15:3-5</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 13:28-31</li>\r\n	<li>Romans 6:3-10, 8:11</li>\r\n	<li>Mark 16:18-19</li>\r\n	<li>Luke 24:50-51</li>\r\n	<li>Acts 1:9-11</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1365, 298, '_core_belief_2', 'field_51e477ec02d1d'),
(1366, 298, 'core_belief_3', 'We believe in a born-again experience from the old life in Adam to the new life in Jesus Christ.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>John 3:3</li>\r\n	<li>1 Corinthians 15:22</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1367, 298, '_core_belief_3', 'field_51e4781602d1e'),
(1368, 298, 'core_belief_4', 'We believe Jesus took on the nature of man and was tempted, yet he never yielded to sin and as a result abolished death.\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 2:16</li>\r\n	<li>Hebrews 4:15</li>\r\n	<li>II Timothy 1:10</li>\r\n</ul>'),
(1369, 298, '_core_belief_4', 'field_51e4783f02d1f'),
