(230, 1, '2013-07-15 17:54:35', '2013-07-16 00:54:35', 'Come as you are. We believe in a House of Prayer for all of God’s people, where God is no respector of persons (Acts 10:34, Isaiah 56:7).', 'What should I wear?', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'what-should-i-wear', '', '', '2013-07-15 17:54:35', '2013-07-16 00:54:35', '', 0, 'http://gac.bkc-stage.com/?post_type=faq&#038;p=230', 0, 'faq', '', 0) ;
